headline: Is Align Technology Stock Underperforming the S&P 500?
summary: Align Technology has underperformed the S&P 500 over the past year, but analysts are cautiously optimistic about the stock’s prospects.

headline: 1 Healthcare Stock for Long-Term Investors and 2 We Avoid
summary: Personal health and wellness is one of the many secular tailwinds for healthcare companies. Those leading the charge have realized strong financial performance, and over the past six months, the industry’s 13.5% return has closely followed the S&P 500.
